{"tid":2173754,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC][U29][Heart of Deimos] Warframe - 戰甲神兵 我地又死灰復燃","createTime":"2020-08-25T12:11:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T01:43:08.000Z","uid":38888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"226a403e5f74b9ebddf088cd33a6a87b30ee919a","tid":2173754,"uid":38888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:11:14.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/173042411809931265/747041869741031434/gdngjv6i5ch51.png \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F173042411809931265%2F747041869741031434%2Fgdngjv6i5ch51.png%20&h=6b590159&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>呢個POST係開黎<del>搵人同on9樓主打機</del>搵人一齊玩WARFRAME同提供新手情報</strong><br />\n<br />\n所以呢到係<span class=\"red\">會</span>放兩個仲叫有人既Discord Link但公會Golden Prime就<span class=\"red\">唔會</span>再收人, 因為已經小圈子到爆曬人. <span class=\"green\"><strong>歡迎大家入黎搵人打機/post 你地既discord. </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n交易/集中討論/LIHKG公會 可以去番下面傳送門<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2104777/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2104777/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記住唔一定要有MIC <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知點解好多人以為要有Mic先入得RC群一齊玩<br />\n<strong>最重要係大家一齊玩，吹下水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有嘢大家開心些牙，有問題大家一齊解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">希望大家入來做朋友，玩到熟絡</span></span> </strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">Golden Warframe Discord群</span> </strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/649gdCh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2F649gdCh&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=6b91a063\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/649gdCh</a><br />\n呢個係老手/棄GAME/打公仔/打工仔群, <br />\n所以正常番工時間/非大更<span class=\"red\">唔會有人</span><br />\n<br />\n藍絲/狗/五毛唔洗入黎, 3萬支那肺炎 THX<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">集合啦! 一齊玩WARFRAME Discord群</span> </strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://discord.gg/cpXyWxY \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FcpXyWxY%20&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=18847e60\" target=\"_blank\">http://discord.gg/cpXyWxY </a><br />\n本群組介紹: 想聚集和招收仍在遊玩WARFRAME的香港玩家互相交流， 群內都是一班友善可愛的香港人，一起互相幫忙和遊玩。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"blue\">官方網頁</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://warframe.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwarframe.com%2F&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=c4ec2ac1\" target=\"_blank\">http://warframe.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"green\">官方 Fan Page</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/PlayWarframe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPlayWarframe&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=66704d96\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/PlayWarframe</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"purple\">Discord 官方網頁 (RC 收皮)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://discordapp.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscordapp.com%2F&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=e8fa2e02\" target=\"_blank\">https://discordapp.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">Warframe Wiki</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://warframe.wikia.com/wiki/WARFRAME_Wiki \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwarframe.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2FWARFRAME_Wiki%20&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=d1b99961\" target=\"_blank\">http://warframe.wikia.com/wiki/WARFRAME_Wiki </a><br />\n<br />\n水人Prime Trailer<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QACf0yN5eYU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQACf0yN5eYU&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=0768bb0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QACf0yN5eYU</a><br />\n<br />\nTennoCon 2020<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qAKq6sOO0tM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqAKq6sOO0tM&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=40258744\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qAKq6sOO0tM</a><br />\n<br />\n<del>                          </del><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/warframe-credit-digital-extremes@2000x1270-696x442.jpg \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nme.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fwarframe-credit-digital-extremes%402000x1270-696x442.jpg%20&h=99b9e0df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"orange\">U 2 9 Heart of Deimos <br />\n更新重點</span></span> (25/08/2020 PMT = HK 26/08/2020)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"purple\"> Helminth </span> &ndash; Helminth解蠕蟲, 可以食件普通甲, 然後俾招技第二隻甲。即係又要farm 甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"blue\"> XAKU </span> - 破碎甲(社群甲), 第二隻由玩家社群(癡線佬)設計並勝出既戰甲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"green\">新Open world Deimos </span> &ndash; 新Content畀玩家farm farm farm 同HEA時間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\"> Inaros PRIME</span> &ndash; 沙人Prime呀!!!!! 正呀屌你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> [/b]<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><del>                          </del><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/BymxMmy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBymxMmy.png&h=f464b30c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\">Golden Prime</span> </strong> <br />\n<br />\n人均0.1隻Excalibur Prime既滿人/ 會長臭貓都棄左GAME舊登公會, <br />\n但On9樓主想開HK Alliance, 整光時Alliance Icon, 有意可以入黎針針佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/579MfyO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F579MfyO.png&h=9944f4ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HJbVMdb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHJbVMdb.png&h=7176bc02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n </p><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<del>                          </del><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">本帖目錄</span></span><br />\n請善用 Ctrl + F 搜索功能 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">遊戲特色</span></strong><br />\n新手須知<br />\n常見問題<br />\n新手目標[/center]<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><del>                          </del><br />\n<img src=\"https://n9e5v4d8.ssl.hwcdn.net/uploads/642e7e91f13e3410f52409eb05a962ac.png \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn9e5v4d8.ssl.hwcdn.net%2Fuploads%2F642e7e91f13e3410f52409eb05a962ac.png%20&h=54dfb376&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"maroon\">遊戲特色</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"blue\">[size=5]<strong>一．裝備多，各有特色（好似係）</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家<span class=\"red\">U28</span>，戰甲有 <strong>43</strong> 件，武器超過 <strong>390</strong> 樣<br />\n寵物加埋哨兵有 <strong>30</strong> 隻，哨兵武器有 <strong>18</strong> 樣<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>弓弩槍矛刀劍匕爪盾斧拳錘鞭拐鐮</strong></span>&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n樣樣齊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">榴彈、火箭、大炮、飛標、飛鋸、激光、噴火槍</span></strong>&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n乜春都有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>地、風、水、火、冰、毒、電、獵龍、犀牛、精靈<br />\n忍者、死神、獵人、狂戰士、聖騎士、快槍手、吟遊詩人</strong></span>&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n重有好多好多, 你中意邊件戰甲就玩邊件 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"blue\"><strong>二．唔洗畀錢，打機賺點</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n認真，你可以完全唔洗畀錢玩<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"green\"><strong>戰甲神兵所有裝備、道具、Mod 都唔洗畀錢就打到</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左要畀錢買<strong><span class=\"red\">武器／戰甲位</span></strong>之外，就得<strong>裝飾</strong>要畀錢買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你重可以同玩家<span class=\"green\"><strong>交易賺白金</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係一個仙都唔洗畀，都玩得好勁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"blue\"><strong>三．兩個字：爽！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n爬牆、跑牆、翻滾、飛踢，你點玩就點玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n硬食、閃避 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、<span class=\"blue\"><strong>潛行</strong></span><br />\n重可以 <span class=\"red\"><strong>殺出一條血路</strong></span> 呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最重要<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>配合隊友技能，一齊合作過關</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></p>"},{"pid":"9e52e0e64c0380a1b0e241e29b4fe887fe09f138","tid":2173754,"uid":38888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:11:39.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><del>                          </del><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">新手須知</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">註冊</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n首先去上面個<span class=\"red\"><strong>官網</strong></span>到註冊先<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">但係註冊之前</span></strong></span><br />\n你可以選擇入 Discord 群是但問一個人 / 問自己朋友仔攞條 Referral Link<br />\n用佢註冊既話, 對方會得到放<strong>武器 / 戰甲既格仔位</strong>同遊戲既 <strong>Mod 卡</strong>送<br />\n而你就會得到<strong><ins>一星期既經驗加乘</ins></strong>, 咁你升裝備同 Rank 就快好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n註冊完當然就 download 隻 game 啦, 咁你更新可能都要 1 ~ 4 個鐘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">設定</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果覺得lag機, 除咗入<strong><span class=\"red\">遊戲裏面調校特效</span></strong>之外<br />\n你重可以試下下面嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n睇下 <strong><span class=\"red\">Launcher 右上角</span></strong>, 撳入去<span class=\"red\"><strong>代表設定既齒輪</strong></span><br />\n關閉 / 開啟 <strong><ins>64-bit 模式</ins></strong><br />\n關閉 / 開啟 <strong><ins>DirectX 11</ins></strong><br />\n關閉 / 開啟 <strong><ins>Multi-threaded rendering</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>如果你鐘意嘅, 可以轉做繁體中文版<br />\n不過英文版會方便 Discord 群咁多位解決你地嘅問題</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">白金</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n初頭送嘅白金, <span class=\"green\"><strong>100% 絕對建議</strong></span>按照以下先後次序去洗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<strong><span class=\"green\">武器 / 戰甲位 &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; 薯仔 &gt; 其他所有嘢</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span class=\"red\">記住, 除咗格仔位同裝飾之外, 其餘所有嘢都唔一定要畀錢</span></ins></strong></p><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><del>                          </del><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\">常見問題</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Warframe <span class=\"red\">入任 load 好慢 / 換裝 lag / 唔知咩事 lag</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 跟上面 <span class=\"green\"><strong>新手須知 &gt; 設定</strong></span> 試下做<br />\n<br />\n2. 唔得就照舊開 <span class=\"navy\"><strong>Warframe Launcher</strong></span> &gt; 右上角撳 <span class=\"green\"><strong>齒輪</strong></span><br />\n3. <span class=\"navy\"><strong>Download Cache</strong></span> 下面, 撳 <span class=\"green\"><strong>Verify</strong></span><br />\n4. 入遊戲裏面試試, 唔得就試埋 <strong><span class=\"green\">Optimize</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n5. 真係唔得, 可以試下到遊戲裏面撳 <strong><span class=\"green\">Escape &gt; Options &gt; Gameplay</span></strong><br />\n6. <span class=\"navy\"><strong>Gameplay </strong></span>下面轉下 <strong><span class=\"green\">Region</span></strong>, 可以試下其他地區<br />\n(P.S. [grey]摺耳貓飛踢[/grey]由亞洲轉去北美, 即刻loading唔再lag)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Discord <span class=\"red\">「沒有路由」 / 0 ping</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 入 Discord。<br />\n2. 睇最底，撳你個名旁邊個<strong><span class=\"green\">齒輪</span></strong>，即係「<span class=\"green\"><strong>使用者設定</strong></span>」。<br />\n3. 睇左邊，入「<span class=\"green\"><strong>語音</strong></span>」。<br />\n4. 睇最頂，入「<span class=\"blue\"><strong>進階</strong></span>」<br />\n5. <span class=\"red\">取消</span>「<strong>Enable Quality of Service High Packet Priority</strong>」<br />\n6. 重開 Discord。</p><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><del>                          </del><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">新手目標</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打完教學, 到底有咩好做? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"purple\">第 1 個目標 : 當然係開晒所有星球既任務</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n你鐘意既, 可以入群搵新手自己慢慢開又得, Online 同鬼佬開又得<br />\n<strong>搵d日日無咩野做得閒到死既人做都可以 </strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>不過注意</strong></span></span>, 唔夠抽, 就唔好勉強, 去以前d星球練兩手先啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"purple\">第 2 個目標 : 緊係搵件自己鐘意既戰甲</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n你可以先去 Wiki 到睇睇咁多種戰甲邊樣你最想玩<br />\n又可以去 Youtube 睇人地玩成點, 先再決定 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過最快當然入Discord群到問番我地既意見啦, 即時俾到答案你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你只係想知<strong><span class=\"large\">邊件最勁</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 我就係到答你 - <del>Rhino</del> <del>Mesa</del> <del>Excalibur</del> <del>Loki</del> <del>mag</del> <span class=\"pink\">PiNk RhInO</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/uycpxjxz0hi31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Fuycpxjxz0hi31.jpg&h=d4825b7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"purple\">第 3 個目標 : 主線任務(Codex Quest)</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n建議新手應該玩返 2 / 3 星期先好做, 唔只係啲任對新手幾難打<br />\n<span class=\"blue\"><strong>等你熟識 Warframe 之後, 你打落都會有氣氛啲</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </p>"},{"pid":"4208dfffafdd1bd16da7f0bd7ec4d9a89d51780c","tid":2173754,"uid":38888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:11:49.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"purple\">第 4 個目標 : 收集需要既Mod</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n夠錢夠材料夠Rank整槍整戰甲, 但係發現得d廢 Mod <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<strong>Mod 有分 Common, Uncommon, Rare, Legendary, Riven 五種稀有度</strong><br />\n一般黎講愈稀有愈有用既, 其實都只係話你知張野有幾難跌姐<br />\n咁當然, 好多必須既 Mod 都係 Rare, 所以都有排你玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"purple\">第 5 個目標 : 升 Mastery Rank</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nMastery Rank 高唔代表勁, 但係代表你可以玩多d武器<br />\n暫時最高係Rank26, 升到 Rank 12 就足夠, 可以買埋集團勢力既專有武器 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左解鎖武器, 仲有<strong>交易次數限制</strong>同埋<strong>武器初始Mod容量</strong><br />\n都係按照你 Mastery Rank 架 [<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"purple\"><strong>第 6 個目標 : 打Nightwave/Alert</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n打Nightwave做咩呀?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">除左裝飾, Warframe 全部裝備都可以打番黎既</span></strong></span><br />\n<span class=\"blue\"> Nightwave/ Alert </span>會有好多冇得買嘅武器打, 一定要留意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗用錢買架, <span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>如果你真係要白金, 可以玩交易賣野</strong></span></span>, 我就是成功的例子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n順便再提一提, <span class=\"green\">白金最好買裝備格仔位</span>, 除非你錢多無地方洗<span class=\"pink\"><span class=\"x-small\">我就是成功的例子</span></span><br />\n<strong>所以, 打啦, 打到有薯仔, 有頭盔, 有武器, 大大力打落去</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </p><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><del>                          </del><br />\n<span class=\"purple\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">等等, 仲有大把野</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">打生存, 打防守, 武器戰甲同 Mod、圖鑑收藏<br />\n去到後期打 Prime 裝, 打 Sortie, 打活動<br />\n裝飾屋企, 扮靚靚, 養寵物, 抽Riven </span></strong><br />\n<span class=\"blue\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>大把野等你玩, 你仲唔快d加入?</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>快d入 Discord 呀</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://g.udn.com.tw/community/img/PSN_PHOTO/chouluchanmydog4w/f_6708983_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fg.udn.com.tw%2Fcommunity%2Fimg%2FPSN_PHOTO%2Fchouluchanmydog4w%2Ff_6708983_1.jpg&h=9d8daba4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://a.fod4.com/misc/Cat Needs Help.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fa.fod4.com%2Fmisc%2FCat%20Needs%20Help.gif&h=0190d288&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/zsghQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzsghQ.gif&h=a958d5b5&s={SIZE}\" /> </p>"},{"pid":"43212207b14b3f57ebe531c5b0f18d8341818a8f","tid":2173754,"uid":38888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:12:07.000Z","msg":"號外<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">DOJO 點解會高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啊寶Where are you</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3GWCngc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3GWCngc.png&h=916bf9c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B7qjABJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB7qjABJ.png&h=c62bfef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太空坦克<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kBhJ2hm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkBhJ2hm.png&h=ecfdb3ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n渣古<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SLW3hRe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSLW3hRe.png&h=ab8a67e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有EVA艦(得入面) <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NKvC6G2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNKvC6G2.png&h=646ea3f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62b265a2e6db8a3cddb4d06d726890dd8e82628b","tid":2173754,"uid":38888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:13:04.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"03eb617bfed3b8844d43980f3bd0f6994ea7b61a","tid":2173754,"uid":146594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0475a1027fae95af592879c21a4da20048752ffb","tid":2173754,"uid":38888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:14:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"06215f1612b5097294be8529e4ba7e192b2d4fbe","tid":2173754,"uid":38888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:14:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"46e9d3c66c3bf5333afcea609e408e9d3146ce64","tid":2173754,"uid":38888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:15:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a1c5b2f94df34f99565bc0f0b03263eb8ff75a8f","tid":2173754,"uid":202051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12: